@node Release @value{PACKAGE}-@value{VERSION}
@unnumberedsubsec Major changes for release @value{PACKAGE}-@value{VERSION}
@cindex release @value{PACKAGE}-@value{VERSION}

This is the fourth separate release from @cite{The OpenSS7 Project} of the
@cite{@value{PACKAGE_TITLE}} package.  This package provides @file{pts} and
@file{ptm} pseudo-terminal drivers, as well as an @file{ldterm} module.
Additional modules are the @file{ptem}, @file{ttcompat} and @file{pckt} modules.
The package contains all the necessary manual pages and other documentation for
terminal and pseudo-terminal components in a separate autoconf tarball.

This release is a maintenance release providing support for recent distributions
and tool chains.

Major features since the last public release are as follows:

@itemize -
@item
Make kernel modules license explicit GPL v2.

@end itemize

